default:
• All recruitment requisition procedure will be worked on after the final approvals by the approval authorities.
  • Requisition form duly completed by immediate supervisor & approved respective department HOD will be submitted to the Company’s chief Coordinator, which will then be submitted to the HR Department after the final approval from the MD.
  • No direct requisition will be entertained for any position without the authorized requisition form.
  • This form is to facilitate the recruitment process through the proper channel by informing the HR Department of their intent to recruit for a position.
  • It is mandatory to fill all of the above details in the Requisition Form, as further recruitment will be preceded as per details provided in the form. Any later changes required by the HOD in the requisition need to be approved by the approval authorities.
  • Recruitment will be done as per the time frame given below:
    • Level 1 (Managerial Positions & Above - 3 months)
    • Level 2 (Asst. Managerial Positions & Below - 2 months)
    • Level 3 (Engineer, Executive, Supervisor Entry Level - 1 month)
